&lt;li&gt;Identify, manage, and mitigate security risks across the data platform, maintaining high standards in all initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and implement methodologies to guarantee the performance, scalability, and quality of our data infrastructure.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
